{"tid":1347971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"721上環開槍 & 元朗警黑合作","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:28:07.000Z","uid":103582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa2817adae78d0b314a51266e24a4c97063afc9","tid":1347971,"uid":103582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"721 上環開槍<br />\n1. 2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR32-nLN989PeIpOXQfHcYBU8f7aw-LRym7XM1ZsGoS5pLngtXIT3T9FAtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR32-nLN989PeIpOXQfHcYBU8f7aw-LRym7XM1ZsGoS5pLngtXIT3T9FAtg&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=21c97dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR32-nLN989PeIpOXQfHcYBU8f7aw-LRym7XM1ZsGoS5pLngtXIT3T9FAtg</a><br />\n<br />\n2.【721即時】<br />\n22:44 警察向示威者開槍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/336543320631999/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fvideos%2F336543320631999%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=4e1a7ce3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/336543320631999/</a><br />\n<br />\n3.【721開槍實錄】<br />\n克警濫暴，我們必定會追究到底。<br />\n林鄭，請爲每滴港人流的血負責。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgodblesshk%2Fvideos%2F583308962199292%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=1f4abfa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e1297545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 警方信德中心對開施放催淚彈驅散示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/392518518062117/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F392518518062117%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=76a1ad79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/392518518062117/</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 22:30【#城大速報 - 本報記者被催淚彈頭擊中！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1106444286213129&amp;id=387603714763860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1106444286213129%26id%3D387603714763860&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=d52bcd49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1106444286213129&amp;id=387603714763860</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗事件影片大整合<br />\n1. 黑警mtr見白衣人調頭走<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/887916731333807/posts/2176272822498185?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F887916731333807%2Fposts%2F2176272822498185%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=df4be16b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/887916731333807/posts/2176272822498185?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 黑警落閘唔比報警<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2883700615005387?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F197517173623758%2Fposts%2F2883700615005387%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=2075234c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2883700615005387?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 民賤聯何君堯同白衣人握手<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/673975979716035/posts/694918787621754?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F673975979716035%2Fposts%2F694918787621754%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=5d0a9abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/673975979716035/posts/694918787621754?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 多名黑警到mtr睇住白衣人走不理<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2959610207413357?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F2959610207413357%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=357f380e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2959610207413357?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 黑警同白衣人有講有笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091741260286?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10156091741260286%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=7eb749b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091741260286?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 有善對待白衣人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2054342341501416/posts/2404814356454211?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2054342341501416%2Fposts%2F2404814356454211%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=0c8c50c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2054342341501416/posts/2404814356454211?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n7. 正苦車載白衣人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/509216622/posts/10156505299006623?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F509216622%2Fposts%2F10156505299006623%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=a66efc08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/509216622/posts/10156505299006623?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n8. 黑警個人fb預告白衣人準備大量滕條打人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1414116366/posts/10219932986741074?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1414116366%2Fposts%2F10219932986741074%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=d10d62dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1414116366/posts/10219932986741074?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n9. 黑警扮瞎撚睇唔到白衣人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2959858797388498?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F2959858797388498%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=a87ff7ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2959858797388498?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n10. 黑警對白衣人及市民差別<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091909035286?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10156091909035286%3Fsfns%3D1&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=dab85a27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091909035286?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n11.元朗打人事件有大肚婆被打到訓低左<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6cXRFR8Uhl4&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e2746c7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4</a><br />\n1:40 追打立場記者<br />\n2:00 圍毆大肚婆<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/660618832/posts/10157546397058833?s=1253604847&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F660618832%2Fposts%2F10157546397058833%3Fs%3D1253604847%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=13b3b9d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/660618832/posts/10157546397058833?s=1253604847&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"0d37abb4d6f84c6cd94af97bd31bce14bf36701c","tid":1347971,"uid":103582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"be9988880ce525c33117b13ffeeaeb9ffda8cbf2","tid":1347971,"uid":48379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:44:30.000Z","msg":"good combination, push"},{"pid":"0109fee93e237fb61d96fcf1c5abb99cd1cb8b77","tid":1347971,"uid":103582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a902f0ee89b5554427cd292518ea042c31afc3f0","tid":1347971,"uid":199709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"上環Video 整合 (粗略) <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a> <br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=c11fad29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=f43145b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=26c17b20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=6a5f4997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=22e97f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=41f17dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=01768859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=67057b42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=3eb1a4d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=20cc9353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=fad2557f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=ba3d8053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?