url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=67057b42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=3eb1a4d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=20cc9353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=fad2557f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=ba3d8053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=c488f78a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=5041a1a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e1297545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n黑警用催淚彈直射向記者 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=d79da7e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=800c28d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n（07.21）譴責警察暴力：記者被催淚彈打中，係直接打中！ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=d79da7e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n7.21民陣大遊行 | 警方平射角度開槍清場 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEsy4jTTOpYI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=75937f4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n有記者直接被催淚彈打中 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTeVHAuMLP4&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=884e6f16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4</a><br />\n有義士腳部中槍 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863977222448%3Fs%3D1279554103%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=99df02ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n【2225 上環】警方施放多枚催淚彈，其後多部警車在警察防線後方鳴笛 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2513792761974182&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=1756499b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182</a><br />\n7.21 催淚彈在人群中爆開 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D446725156177245&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=cb4ee651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245</a><br />\n7.21 無證速龍向記者舉槍 亮警棍威嚇 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=370689103642714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.li